Mother and father were imp√©rial tortured and killed by thalmor when Kerstin was 6 year old. She was send to Riften in Grelod's orphanage where she spend some 10 years before managing succesfully to escape and went to Cyrodiil.
In Bruma, Kerstin found refuge at Olav's Tap and Tack in exchange of a hard work, chopping wood, preparing and serving food, cleaning the inn.......
Sexually harrassed by Olav, at 18, Kerstin went away and return to Bordeciel. On her way to Whiterun she meet a patrol of thalmor, and remembering her parent, she killed all of them. She stayed beetween the dead thalmor, still as a stone, until imperial soldiers found her.
She is now in a carriage on the way to Helgen........... Story to be continued.
